==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Untitled
<hw>Un*ti"tled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
titled; having no title, or appellation of dignity or distinction.</def>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Being without title or right; not entitled.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unto</ent>⟦br⟧
